protein.general_function: Involved in extracellular ligand-gated ion channel activity
protein.specific_function: After binding acetylcholine, the AChR responds by an extensive change in conformation that affects all subunits and leads to opening of an ion-conducting channel across the plasma membrane

go_class.description: excitatory extracellular ligand-gated ion channel activity
